  "factionId": "SM",
  "sourceId": "000000356",
  "legend": "Originally designed on Terra for the task of rooting out burrowing xenos species during the Great Crusade, canny commanders quickly found use for the Termite Assault Drill in tearing through the foundations of enemy bastions or emerging behind barricades or trench lines to lay waste to their defenders.",
  "role": "Dedicated Transports",
